NeuroCore Full Enterprise Simulation & Browser Validation Plan
Objective
Create a comprehensive, end-to-end Enterprise Simulation, Workflow Validation, and Browser Execution Plan for NeuroCore.
This is NOT a feature checklist, unit-test plan, or isolated QA exercise.
The purpose is to simulate a real tenant company operating entirely through NeuroCore and validate whether the platform functions as a complete AI-native enterprise operating system.
The simulation must exercise the entire organization across departments, human employees, Hermes AI Employees, projects, communications, approvals, finance, Google Workspace, organizational memory, timelines, events, governance, and progressive AI autonomy.
The test must prove that NeuroCore works as one integrated enterprise, not as disconnected modules.

